{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_02_03_01",
  "title": "HONNKI \noh! \nMITAI yo!",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――グッズ販売を開始してしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the merchandise sales began",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.6333333732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "ゴホンッ……\n今日はみんなに大事な話があって集まってもらったギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem…\nI have something important to tell you all today‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666666667,
      "endTime": 8.9762356441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1666664364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "なんの話かしら……嫌な予感しかしないんだけど\nあれ？　さくらは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this about…? I have a bad feeling about this.\nHuh? Where's Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666664364,
      "endTime": 18.6404306652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……見かけていないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it… I haven’t seen her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8333331031,
      "endTime": 22.3658048076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5666664364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……特別ボーナス支給の話ではなくて？\nきっと私達が作ったグッズがバカ売れしたんですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… You’re going to give us a special bonus‚ aren’t you?\nI bet the merchandise we made is selling like crazy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5666664364,
      "endTime": 32.2413374188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4333331031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo002.m4a",
      "text": "実は……みんなが作ったグッズを大量発注した結果\n全く売れず大赤字……魚見プロ倒産の危機なんだギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… Although we ordered your merchandise in bulk‚\nit hasn’t sold at all‚ and we’re deep in debt… Gyogyomi Prods is on the verge of bankruptcy‚ gyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4333331031,
      "endTime": 46.2456690711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.466662876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.466662876,
      "endTime": 47.4210166138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9333287797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "倒産って……倒産したら私達アイドルは\nどうなってしまうんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bankruptcy…? If we go bankrupt‚\nwhat will happen to us idols?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333287797,
      "endTime": 54.964689215199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.1666621131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo003.m4a",
      "text": "魚見プロは……海の藻屑となり消えてしまうギョ……\nそして君達アイドルも行き場を失い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyomi Prods will… disappear into the seafoam‚ gyo…\nAnd you idols will have nowhere to go…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1666621131,
      "endTime": 63.836276905000005,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.670227099994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0999990068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "これは……注文票……？\n確かに全然売れてないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… an order form…?\nIt really hasn’t sold at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0999990068,
      "endTime": 71.6111782632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7999990068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……これはこれは……すずにゃんの法被が\n一番売れてないですね、可哀想に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… Well‚ well‚ well… It looks like Suzu-nyan's haori\nis the least popular. Poor thing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7999990068,
      "endTime": 80.894443091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0999990068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼な！　こころのフェイスシールだって\n二番目に売れてないですわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-how rude! Kokoro's face stickers\nare the second least popular!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0999990068,
      "endTime": 87.27891050199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4666656735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "一番と二番には大きな差があるんですー！\n一緒にしないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a big difference between first and second place~!\nDon’t lump us together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4666656735,
      "endTime": 92.6069829228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7999990068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo004.m4a",
      "text": "静まれいっ！　仲間同士で争っても何も生まれないギョ\nわしもこのまま諦める訳にはいかないギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quiet down! Fighting amongst yourselves won’t solve anything‚ gyo!\nI’m not just giving up either‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7999990068,
      "endTime": 102.7312915407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9666697425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私も諦めたくありません！\nでも……どうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to give up either!\nBut… what should we do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9666697425,
      "endTime": 108.0557627601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2666697425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo005.m4a",
      "text": "わしは学んだギョ。いい物を作ってもプロモーションを\nしっかりしないと売れない時代なんだギョ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve learned my lesson‚ gyo. Even if you make good products‚ they won’t sell\nin this day and age if you don’t promote them properly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2666697425,
      "endTime": 116.1930642051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4666733028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_03-gyogyo006.m4a",
      "text": "プロモーション大作戦を始動するギョ！\nさくらギョン、カモンだギョ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re launching Operation Promotion‚ gyo!\nSakura-gyo‚ come on in‚ gyo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4666733028,
      "endTime": 122.9333435299,
      "sfxList": [
