      "text": "みんな……魚見プロを守るために戦おう！\nこの『GYOGYOハット』を被って変身ギョ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… Let’s fight to protect Gyogyomi Prods!\nPut on these ‘GYO-GYO hats’ and transform‚ gyo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8333455644,
      "endTime": 133.1597404084,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
